snippet.title: Dig VR - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Here's a fresh look at Dig VR in this latest trailer for the upcoming simulator game. The trailer showcases how you can customize your machinery, minigames, a map of Diglington town, and, of course, digging! Dig VR will be available on Meta Quest in 2024.
